<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Rest_Server does not currently support optional parameters for REST methods. It currently requires all parameters to be passed to the method.</p>

<p>I have attached a small patch that enables support for optional parameters, and changed the error logic to only throw an error when one or more required parameters are mssing.</p>

    </div>
